{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"will-tile-plum","description":"## Why\nEpic 88ab (elfish-chair-lug) S3. R3 requires BOTH votes on every feature-branch change and on the merge change. The design EXPECTS g2p dispatch to be branch-agnostic but that is unverified — if `gerrit_to_platform.ini` silently filters `feature/*` refs, story changes never earn Verified and every submit blocks with no error signal. ASSUMES epic 1fa8 (smoky-flare-slug) is complete: g2p installed, `gerrit-verify.yaml` exists, two-vote submit requirement active (the epic-level depends_on covers this — do not start before 1fa8 closes).\n\n## What\n- Determine from g2p source/docs whether `gerrit_to_platform.ini` filters dispatch by branch; replace the design expectation with a VERIFIED statement — either the confirmed required `feature/*` config or a confirmed no-config-needed no-op — recorded in the ini spec.\n- Verify `checkout-gerrit-change-action` correctly fetches a MERGE refspec so CI builds the actual merge tree (inherited finding f6a211e0) — run-log evidence.\n- Prove with run-log evidence: (a) a `feature/*` patchset-created event triggers `gerrit-verify.yaml`; (b) a merge change into main gets CI on the merge tree; (c) Verified RE-RUNS (does not carry) on a re-merge (MERGE_FIRST_PARENT_UPDATE patchset); (d) `concurrency: cancel-in-progress` behaves sanely across concurrent branch + merge changes.\n\n## Scope\ng2p config + workflow verification + evidence only. No label/ACL config (S1), no bot code (S2), no doc prose beyond the ini spec (S4).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Verified statement on g2p branch filtering recorded (config or no-op), with source/doc citation, in the ini spec\n- [ ] Run-log evidence: feature/* patchset triggers gerrit-verify.yaml and casts Verified\n- [ ] Run-log evidence: merge change gets CI on the actual merge tree via the merge refspec\n- [ ] Run-log evidence: Verified re-runs on a re-merge; no carry observed\n- [ ] Concurrency behavior across branch + merge changes documented with a run example","id":"2e8a-1a3b-66bf-4cd1","parent_id":"88ab-7052-8850-46d4","priority":2,"tags":["gerrit","feature-branch","ci","gate"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"S3: CI (Verified) coverage on feature branches + merge changes — g2p dispatch verified"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782964835771375001,"uuid":"93cdfc2b-0f83-4fd6-84d8-5050d5c2f231"}